snippet.textDisplay: From Chandigarh to Mansara, we have unique talents. Despite the fact that Indian coke studio artists are brilliant, this music represents the true nature of Pakistani talent with choreography and music beats well synchronized with the singers, something that we don't see in Indian coke studio. Shafi makes this song extra special by adding his unique funk style to it in order to make this song extra special. Pakistan Zindabad
